@startuml lkmSasanga_fas-web-app

[Firebase Hosting] as FH
[Web Browser] as WB
[React App] as RA
[Backend API] as API

package "React Components" {
  [App]
  [Login]
  [InputControl]
  [RequestData]
  [Charts]
  [UI Components]
}

WB --> FH : Access
FH --> RA : Serve
RA --> [App] : Render
[App] --> [Login] : Route
[App] --> [InputControl] : Route
[InputControl] --> [RequestData] : Use
[RequestData] --> API : HTTP Requests
[Charts] --> [UI Components] : Use

note right of FH : Deployment platform
note right of RA : Client-side routing
note right of [App] : Component-based architecture
note right of API : Data fetching and processing

@enduml